These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
City: san-francisco, miami, prague
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, alhambra, oliveros
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an even position##4
2. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
3. the old-henry-smoker is the person traveling to miami##1
4. the person traveling to prague is on the far left##1
5. the alhambra-smoker is the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| City   | prague | san-francisco | miami |
| Cigar    | alhambra    | oliveros | old-henry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, prince, bolivar
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, hip-hop, salsa
1. the cain-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is in an even position##4
3. the fan of salsa is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Cigar       | prince | bolivar | cain |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | hip-hop     | reggae        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
3 different games are played: domino, monopoly, canasta
The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, firefighter, videographer
1. the person playing domino is on the right of the pilot##1
2. the firefighter is on the left of the pilot##1
3. the person playing monopoly is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Game         | canasta     | monopoly | domino |
| Job   | firefighter | pilot     | videographer  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, boat, van
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, blue, orange
1. the person driving the boat is the person who likes blue##1
2. the person driving the bike is the person who likes orange##1
3. the person driving the boat is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Transport   | van | boat  | bike  |
| Color         | black  | blue | orange |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, red, black
City: prague, colone, rome
1. the person who likes black is between the person who likes aquamarine and the person traveling to prague##2
2. the person who likes red is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Color         | aquamarine   | black | red    |
| City   | colone | rome     | prague |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, bluemaster, fonseca
City: paris, marseilles, rome
1. the cain-smoker is the person traveling to marseilles##1
2. the person traveling to rome is the bluemaster-smoker##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | fonseca | cain   |
| City   | rome     | paris    | marseilles |

