.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola, fanta
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, aquamarine, white
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking sprite is between the person who likes white and the person drinking fanta##2
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
4. the person who likes purple is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Beverage   | fanta | sprite | cola |
| Color           | aquamarine         | purple         | white |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, march, january
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, animation, fantasy
1. the person watching superhero movies is between the person watching animation movies and the person who's birthday is in june##2
2. the person watching fantasy movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Birthday   | march | january | june |
| Movie-Genre    | animation    | superhero | fantasy     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, lemonade, tea
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, iris, amaryllis
1. the person who growsamaryllis is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Beverage   | tea   | lemonade  | mirinda  |
| Flower         | amaryllis | iris | balloon-flower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, ambient, pop
3 different pets are kept: snake, dog, fish
1. the owner of the snake is on the right of the fan of pop##1
2. the owner of the fish is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the fish is on the right of the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | pop      | ambient |
| Pet       | dog | fish | snake   |

