.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
3 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, guinea-pig
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, lily, aconite
1. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the person who growszinnia is the owner of the lizard##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Pet   | guinea-pig  | cat | lizard   |
| Flower         | lily | aconite   | zinnia |

