.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
3 different games are played: backgammon, mah-jongg, whist
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, boat, car
1. the person playing whist is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person driving the boat##2
2. the person playing mah-jongg is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person playing whist is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Game   | mah-jongg | whist | backgammon |
| Transport     | taxi    | car  | boat   |

