.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, lawyer, social-worker
There are 3 different nationalities: german, dutch, chinese
1. the social-worker is on the right of the accountant##1
2. the dutch is on the left of the german##1
3. the dutch is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
4. the social-worker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Job   | accountant  | social-worker     | lawyer |
| Nationality   | dutch | german | chinese    |

