.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-16::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee, soy-milk
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, golf, rugby
1. the person who's sport is rugby is the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage          | soy-milk | milk | coffee  |
| Sport   | rugby      | volleyball  | golf |

