.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, software-developer, social-worker
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, august, november
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the engineer##1
2. the engineer is in the middle##1
3. the social-worker is the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Job         | social-worker | engineer   | software-developer |
| Birthday   | august   | february | november      |

