.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, amaryllis, bellflower
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, hip-hop, pop
1. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an odd position##4
3. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Flower      | balloon-flower | amaryllis | bellflower |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | pop          | techno |

