.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, prince, alhambra
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, subway
1. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the subway is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
3. the alhambra-smoker is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the roller is on the right of the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Cigar     | prince  | alhambra   | old-henry |
| Transport   | subway | roller | motorbike       |

 